description:
Bloomberg Markets with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson. GUEST: Yelena Shulyatyeva Senior US Economist Bloomberg Intelligence Discussing the economy and markets with Bloomberg Stocks Editor Dave Wilson, who also discusses his Chart of the Day "U.S. link between stocks, politics seen as spurious."
